### 🔧 Installation & Setup

#### Requirements
- PHP 8.0+
- MySQL 5.7+
- Composer for dependencies
- Web server (Apache/Nginx)

#### Database Setup
```sql
-- Ensure pages table exists
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS pages (
    id BIGINT UNSIGNED AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    slug VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    content TEXT NOT NULL,
    content_format VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'markdown',
    namespace VARCHAR(50) DEFAULT '',
    created_by BIGINT UNSIGNED NULL,
    updated_by BIGINT UNSIGNED NULL,
    created_at TIMESTAMP NULL,
    updated_at TIMESTAMP NULL,
    INDEX idx_namespace_slug (namespace, slug)
);

-- Ensure page_history table exists
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS page_history (
    id BIGINT UNSIGNED AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    page_id BIGINT UNSIGNED NOT NULL,
    user_id BIGINT UNSIGNED NULL,
    content TEXT NOT NULL,
    comment TEXT NULL,
    created_at TIMESTAMP NULL,
    INDEX idx_page_created (page_id, created_at)
);
```

### 🎯 Usage

#### Creating a Page
1. Navigate to `/pages/create`
2. Fill in the page title and content
3. Select namespace (optional)
4. Choose content format (Markdown recommended)
5. Add edit summary (optional)
6. Submit the form
7. Page will be created and redirect to the new page

#### Example Page Creation
```bash
curl -X POST https://local.islam.wiki/pages \
  -d "title=My Test Page" \
  -d "content=# My Test Page\n\nThis is a test page." \
  -d "namespace=" \
  -d "comment=Initial page creation" \
  -d "content_format=markdown"
```

